a_n, n \ge 0,
a_0 = 2,
n \ge 0, a_{n+1} = \sqrt{a_n + 1}.
n \ge 0, a_n > \frac{1+\sqrt{5}}{2}.
n \ge 0, a_n > a_{n+1}.
x^2 - x - 1 < 0
\frac{1-\sqrt{5}}{2} < x < \frac{1+\sqrt{5}}{2}.
k
a_k\gt \dfrac{1+\sqrt{5}}{2}
a_{k+1}\gt  \dfrac{1+\sqrt{5}}{2}
a_{k+1}^2=a_k+1\gt \dfrac{1+\sqrt{5}}{2}+1=\dfrac{3+\sqrt{5}}{2}=\left(\dfrac{1+\sqrt{5}}{2}\right)^2.
